  "texts": [
    "This feature is currently inactive in the UI but is on the roadmap for future releases.",
    "Data points are standardized in the CONCEPT_DIMENSION table, utilizing globally recognized classifications like international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems (ICD-10), LOINC, and SNOMED-CT for interoperability, promoting data consistency and exchangeability across health care systems.",
    "We manage user access via the USER_MANAGEMENT and USER_PATIENT_LOOKUP tables, controlling data access and permissions, ensuring data are only accessible to authorized users.",
    "To facilitate quality management, a dedicated CQL_FACT table stores CQL 19 rules and their JSON ELM representations.",
    "The CONCEPT_CQL_LOOKUP table links these rules to clinical concepts in the CONCEPT_DIMENSION."
  ],
